==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[give]] [[him|'em]] [[enough]] [[rope]]'''

# {{idiom}} Allow one to [[function]] [[unhindered]], or [[without]] further overbearing [[oversight]].

===Synonyms===
* [[cut one some slack]] / [[cut him some slack]]

===Usage notes===
The common rejoinder/corollary is: "Give 'em enough rope, and he'll hang himself.

